@samp{--map @var{map-file}} or @samp{--rgr_map @var{map-file}}@*
@samp{--rgr @var{key}=@var{val}} (multiple invocations allowed)@*
@samp{--rnr=@var{wgt_thr}} or @samp{--rgr_rnr=@var{wgt_thr}} or 
