@math{@var{prc} < 0}.
For @math{@var{ppc} = 3} or @math{@var{ppc} = -2}, for example, we have
@math{@var{scale} = 1024} and @math{@var{scale} = 1/128}.}
zeroes the greatest number of significand bits consistent with
the desired precision.

